text: Willi Schreyer (9 September 1914 - 2 May 2002) was an Austrian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1914 births Category:2002 deaths Category:Austrian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Austria Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Salzburg
